actions.message:
.AddUser - Adds a user to Tickt/Order
.Active - Sets Ticket/Order As Active
.Manage - Makes Ticket/Order For Only Managment/Support Team Can See
.togglelog - (OwnerOnly)
.Par - Deletes User From Ticket/Order
.Inactive - Sets Ticket/Order to Inactive
.Supportsetup - (Owneronly)
.Staff - Gives User Staff Role (OwnerOnly)
.Reboot - Reboots Bot (OwnerOnly)
.Staff - Adds User To Staff DataBase (OwnerOnly)
.Dev - Adds User To Developer DataBase (OwnerOnly)
.Kick - Kicks User From Server
.Ban - Bans User From Server
.Purge - Deletes Messages
.Warn - Warns User
.Warnings - Shows how much warnings user has
